            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "8nVT3",
              "name": "usageDesc",
              "fill": "$--color-text-primary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 804,
              "content": "全般的には原則Bodyを使い、見出しや補足分、その他UIに他の定義を使う。\nBodyとNoteの行間の定義は複数あり、150%（normal）をデフォルトとする。レイアウトの都合にあわせて*-narrow（175%）、*-tight（125%）を使い分ける。",
              "lineHeight": "$--line-height-relaxed",
              "fontFamily": "Plus Jakarta Sans",
              "fontSize": "$--font-size-md",
              "fontWeight": "$--font-weight-regular"
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "W8a4B",
              "name": "nameUsageTable",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "$--color-bg-primary",
              "layout": "vertical",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "550vI",
                  "name": "nuHeader",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "$--teal-50",
                  "cornerRadius": [
                    4,
                    4,
                    0,
                    0
                  ],
                  "gap": 8,
                  "padding": [
                    12,
                    16
                  ],
